GOAL

Shoot the ball into the basket!!

You have 5 chances to accomplish the task.
The lesser chances you take, the more you score.

KEYS:

d - move the canon left
a - move the canon right
w - increase the angle of canon (wrt to horizontal)
s - decrease the angle of canon (wrt to horizontal)

UP - to increase the initial shooting speed.
DOWN - to decrease the initial shooting speed.
(You can view the speed level on the screen )

Good Luck!!